title: ► Jessica Lange wins The Emmys 2014 - 'Outstanding Lead Actress Miniseries Movie'
author: American Horror Story 10
comment: Sarah was happier than Jessica, such a great moment, and I think Sarah was up for the same award. Great actresses, I love the show.

To all of those who loved Lange on AHS, go check out Country, Frances, Tootsie, Music Box and Blue Sky. She's an amazing, timeless actress. Moreover, she's elegant and so BEAUTIFUL for a woman her age. I love everything about her, most especially her quirkiness, her shyness.
It's the theme song for the show, only a less creepier version. Unfortunately... bwaaahahahaaaaa!
when Sarah was happier than Jessica, Queens
OMG.  truly love, Love, LOVE her!!!  :-)  :-)  :-)
description: Liev Schreiber and Kerry Washington present the Emmy for Outstanding Lead Actress in a Miniseries or Movie to JESSICA LANGE (AMERICAN HORROR STORY) at the 66th Primetime Emmy Awards.
